        <p>in abstract class Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract in function quote() lines #871-873  is not effectivelly used recursive call.
It is not needed to call recursive function for not array wars. So it should be replaced by:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
  if (is_array($val)) {
    $val = $this-&gt;quote($val, $type);
  } else {
    $val = $this-&gt;_quote($val);
  }
</code></pre>

